{
  "stem": "5799.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We both were trained in ballet, which helped me later on during the war, because I entertained all the peasants.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We played the piano.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "My mother played the piano and sang.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And my father played the concertina.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We were never punished, as I think back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We were never yelled at, as I think back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I never doubted that I was loved, although my mother worked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But looking back at it, I realized that I envied my girlfriends who had a mother constantly and mine was busy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I miss them dearly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I find it hard to pray to God, but I speak to my parents daily on my walks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I speak to my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Their birthdays are a torment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And no matter how old one gets and how much you have in life-- and I have my rewards-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you never can forget what was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "It haunts you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "You might call it-- what do you call it in English-- the Holocaust Syndrome.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I suffer from it, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I dream nightly, or if not nightly I am a habitual insomniac.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Because I have a dream that I'm running with both of my children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And you must know that one of my cousins perished like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And on my right hand side is my older daughter, Anita, and my left hand side is my little one, five years younger, the same difference as between my sister and I, Ozelle.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And behind us, I smell the Nazi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "They smelled with tobacco.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "I can smell any soldier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I know their smells.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And I hear his boots behind me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And lo and behold, I come to a big trench.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's full of bodies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, OK, you can live.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
